data.description: ***SELLER WILLING TO CONTRIBUTE TO BUYER RATE BUY DOWN, Seller is MOTIVATED to sell*** Welcome to 828 2nd St, a very welcoming home located in the heart of Ogden, Utah. This charming property offers a perfect blend of comfort and accessibility, making it an ideal place to call home! Step inside this inviting abode, and you'll immediately feel the warm embrace of a welcoming atmosphere. The open and spacious living area is perfect for hosting gatherings with family and friends or enjoying cozy nights in with loved ones. The yard is a retreat, offering a perfect space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Convenience is a highlight of this property, with easy access to nearby amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. Commuting is a breeze, thanks to the property's proximity to major roadways, making it an ideal location for those seeking a balance between urban living and suburban tranquility. Don't miss the chance to make 828 2nd St your new home. Embrace the convenience and warmth of this inviting property in Ogden, Utah. Schedule your private tour today and unlock the door to a life of comfort and ease.    Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from MLS tax data.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
